<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Document</title>
	<style type="text/css">
		html, body {
			max-width: 700px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
		h1 {
			text-align: center;
		}
		
		ul li {
			padding-bottom: 1em;
		}

		table ul {
			list-style: none;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
		}
	
		table ul li {
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
		}

		table tr{
			vertical-align: top;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<header>
	<h1>**frontyard library**</h1>
		<h2>
			<form action="/" method="GET">
				<a href="/about">About</a> | 
				<a href="/">Collection</a> | 
				<a href="/subjects">Subjects</a> | 
				<a href="/authors">Authors</a> 
			
				<label for="query"></label><input type="text" name="query"/>
				<button type="submit">Quick Search</button>
			</form>
		</h2>
	</header>
	<hr>
	{+content/}
	<hr>
	<footer>
		<p><strong>We acknowledge that frontyard meets on Aboriginal land - the Cadigal Wangal people of the Eora are the traditional custodians of the land. We pay our respects to elders past and present.</strong></p>
		<hr>
		<p>This online catalogue is a work in progress. It is proudly opensource and available on Github - <a href="https://github.com/e-e-e/frontyard-library-catalogue">fork it here</a>. We welcome contributors.</p>
		<p>If you would like to see a feature added, or want to suggest changes, <a href="mailto:info@frontyardprojects.org">get in touch</a>.</p>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>
